App Name

FoodBridge

Tagline

“Bridging Surplus Food to Those in Need.”

1️⃣ About the App

FoodBridge is a smart platform that connects food donors, NGOs, and volunteers to redistribute surplus food efficiently and reduce food waste.

The system uses AI prediction, location matching, and real-time notifications to ensure food reaches people in need quickly.

2️⃣ App Concept

FoodBridge acts as a bridge between:

Food Donors
(Restaurants, Hotels, Events)

⬇

FoodBridge Platform

⬇

NGOs & Shelters

⬇

People in Need

3️⃣ Main Features of FoodBridge
1️⃣ Donor Module

Upload surplus food

Set pickup time

Track donation history

2️⃣ NGO Module

View nearby food donations

Accept donation requests

Manage storage capacity

3️⃣ Volunteer Module

Receive pickup notifications

Navigate to donor location

Deliver food to NGO

4️⃣ AI Prediction

Predict surplus food quantity

Reduce food spoilage

5️⃣ Smart Matching

Find nearest NGO automatically

6️⃣ Impact Dashboard

Shows:

