9️⃣ AI Prediction Module

Predict surplus food using machine learning.

Example Python code:

import pandas as pd
from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression

data = pd.read_csv("food_data.csv")

X = data[['event_size']]
y = data['surplus_food']

model = LinearRegression()
model.fit(X,y)

prediction = model.predict([[200]])

print("Predicted surplus:", prediction)
🔟 Smart Matching Engine

The system finds the nearest NGO.

Steps:

Get donor location

Check NGO locations

Calculate distance

Select nearest NGO

Python library used:

geopy
